title: Who is this Cynicatt person?
body:
I've noticed all the usual GD betas jerking them. I remember them from old GD, but they weren't paid attention to much then. When did they become ever GD beta's wet dream?

edit: I want to make it clear that it is not their fault that this happened and I don't think negatively of them. Betas gonna do what betas gonna do.

edit 2: Even now this thead will have an abnormal amount of views and replies from their beta whiteknights. Some of them are actually posting below .3.
